      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON PRESIDENT (8) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 17.57 beating Zipping Deloris. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. DYNAMIC REBEL (4) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 1 last run (17.58) at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Expecting another good run. SHE'S SILKY (1) jumped from this box and went down narrowly when a 0.8 lengths second (17.61) in a Mix 3/4 at this track over 300m latest. Rates a key player. MAJESTIC TYSON (6) cannot be left out after placing last start.",
